        "\n",
        "## 13.15 Common mistakes\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Forgetting to center the data.** The zero-frequency component can dominate the periodogram.\n",
        "2. **Interpreting trend as periodicity.** Strong trend creates low-frequency power.\n",
        "3. **Confusing frequency and period.** Frequency is cycles per time step; period is time steps per cycle.\n",
